  "title": "How to implement a callback after execution of a widget",
  "body": "Hi, \r\nI'm using a rangeSlider to filter the hits and I would like to display the interval price chosen by the user\r\n<img width=\"334\" alt=\"price-interval\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/24573118/21195570/9e80a0d4-c234-11e6-9785-913178940507.png\">\r\n\r\nTo achieved that, I think I need a callback on the currentRefinedValues widget. Do you know How I could do that and if it is my best option?\r\n",
